  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797610/extras/a302ab5d222df6e82acb980cd6b78f67.avif?t=1743187648\" width=500 height=100 /></span><br><br>Barro 22 is a racing game with a toy car / go kart style, the next gen for Barro Racing now with the tracks from the first game of the series.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 25 Race tracks<br></li><li> 7 new vehicles<br></li><li> Time Trial<br></li><li> Single player (Casual race vs Bots)<br></li><li> Multiplayer (split screen, up to 4 players)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797610/extras/a302ab5d222df6e82acb980cd6b78f67.avif?t=1743187648\" width=500 height=100 /></span><br><br>Barro 22 is a racing game with a toy car / go kart style, the next gen for Barro Racing now with the tracks from the first game of the series.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 25 Race tracks<br></li><li> 7 new vehicles<br></li><li> Time Trial<br></li><li> Single player (Casual race vs Bots)<br></li><li> Multiplayer (split screen, up to 4 players)</li></ul>",
